WEBVTT

00:00:00.079 --> 00:00:01.873
Možda mislite da trebate mlijeko,

00:00:01.914 --> 00:00:03.833
koje je bogato kalcijem i vitaminom D,

00:00:03.875 --> 00:00:07.420
da biste imali jake i zdrave kosti.

00:00:07.420 --> 00:00:11.966
Ta je ideja prodala mnogo mlijeka
kroz godine,

00:00:12.008 --> 00:00:15.511
ali nije znanstveno točna.

00:00:15.553 --> 00:00:16.763
(Glazba)

00:00:16.763 --> 00:00:18.306
[Body Stuff s dr. Jen Gunter]

00:00:19.182 --> 00:00:23.102
Za shvaćanje zdravlja kostiju,
nije dovoljno u obzir uzeti samo mlijeko.

00:00:23.144 --> 00:00:25.146
Počnimo otpočetka.

00:00:25.188 --> 00:00:27.231
Odrasla osoba ima 260 kostiju

00:00:27.273 --> 00:00:30.068
koje tvore glavni dio kostura.